PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister responsible for the Federal Office of Regional Development - Quebec to enter into a SUPPLEMENTARY AGREEMENT that will postpone the expiry date of the CANADA-QUEBEC SUBSIDIARY AGREEMENT ON THE ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT OF THE REGIONS OF QUEBEC until March 31, 1995, and harmonize its provisions with the regional development policy of Quebec.
